# Daemon/CI-rebuilt data artifacts: a text-level merge conflict on these is
# meaningless (the whole file is regenerated every run) — resolve by keeping
# whichever build is FRESHER, via scripts/wca_merge_freshest.py. This is a
# scoped mitigation for the recurring "two builders raced this file" conflict
# class (2026-07-04); see that script's docstring for why it's this and not
# the bigger untrack-from-git change.
#
# Contributors: run `bash scripts/wca_install_merge_driver.sh` once (adds the
# driver to this repo's local .git/config; git does not read driver commands
# from .gitattributes itself for security reasons).
